#: ../../user/templates/debian/debian.rst:122 ac492f3d9f624ebcbfdf4b96278da4a9
msgid "Unattended Upgrades"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/templates/debian/debian.rst:125 9dc6bcbd1a3944bd973cb882dcfdf03b
msgid ""
"Some users have noticed that on upgrading Debian templates, the "
"``unattended-upgrade`` package is installed. This package is pulled in as"
" part of a Recommend chain, and can be purged. The lesson is that you "
"should carefully look at what is being installed to your system, "
"particularly if you run ``dist-upgrade``."
msgstr ""

